#, fuzzy
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Since usually a <quote>byte</quote> is the smallest common unit for data "
#~ "on computers each <quote>character</quote> you see on a screen is "
#~ "represented by exactly one byte. Each byte can stand for a value from 0 "
#~ "to 255 and therefore you are able to display up to 256 different "
